<L>__{interior sabena president's office. day}
<A>__{the sabena president and two vps sit on couches.}
<C>__{president}
<D>__{if british airways abandons the route we should bid for it.}
<A>__{his intercom buzzes, he's annoyed then.}
<C>__{secretary }
