<C>__{paul}
<D>__{now we have eight hundred guests and one hundred staff. i have ten minutes left. i wish i could have done more, sir. please, thank all my friends at sabena. you have been good to me and my family.}
<C>__{president}
<P>__{(panicked) paul, wait, wait, i'm going to}
<D>__{put you on hold for one minute, stay on the phone.}
